heading: Suvodeep Majumder  passes Ph.D. defense
summary:
Suvodeep Majumder  passes his thesis, "Exploitation of Repeated Structures for SW Analytics":
- 3*fse, 2*msr, 1*(icse,ist,tosem,emse)
- Distinguished paper FSE'21
- Next step:postdoc at Columbia with Baishakhi Ray

heading: Automated SE journal (edited by Prof. Menzies (CSC, NCSU))'s impact has  doubled.
summary: The impact factor of the Automated SE journal (edited by Prof. Menzies (CSC, NCSU))'s has  doubled fro  1.6 (last year) to 3.4 (now).
